name: Time Travel Paranoia
description:
After accepting the mission to apprehend someone rumoured to have successfully cloned themselves you're entrusted with an artifact that can allegedly alter time. Does it truly work?

My submission to the University of Birmingham Spring Game Jam 2021.
Art Kit provided by UoB GDS Discord server.
Sound FX used: https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/audio/sound-fx/retro-sound-effects-22153
